# TypeSpec generated output — ignore everything except hand-written customisations
Azure.AI.AgentServer.Responses.Contracts/src/TypeSpec/tsp-output/**
# Allow the Custom/ folder through (hand-written partial classes)
!Azure.AI.AgentServer.Responses.Contracts/src/TypeSpec/tsp-output/src/
!Azure.AI.AgentServer.Responses.Contracts/src/TypeSpec/tsp-output/src/Custom/
!Azure.AI.AgentServer.Responses.Contracts/src/TypeSpec/tsp-output/src/Custom/**

# Python bytecode
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# npm lockfiles are committed to ensure reproducible installs

# Copilot + Spec Kit — local-only files (never committed)
# Bootstrap with: ./scripts/Bootstrap-Copilot.ps1
.specify/
.speckit/
.github/
specs/

.specs/
